snippet.title: Amber Heard CONDRICTS Herself! PROVES Johnny Depp was RIGHT | The HollyVibe
snippet.description:
Amber Heard CONDRICTS Herself! PROVES Johnny Depp was RIGHT | The HollyVibe

Welcome toThe HollyVibe. We make interesting videos about Hollywood in English. We give you a closer look in the lives of celebrities like Kanye West, Ed Sheeran, The Rock, Jay Z, Selena Gomez, Kylie Jenner, Kim Kardashian, Rihanna and 100s more.

Amber Heard keeps making life much harder for herself by contradicting herself in the eyes of the law. The Johnny Depp Amber Heard case rages on and is still a hot piece of celebrity news. But Amber Heard might have really buried herself this time.  

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. Her team has been working tirelessly in order to back up her side, however Johnny Depp seems to have made the attempt to strike back.

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnny

We tell you interesting things about these Hollywood celebrities that you may have never heard before.

Cheers!
